 e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic003231.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#martaf #AA\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Cw n=\"5\">Ἐπαφρό\u003Csupplied reason=\"omitted\">δ\u003C/supplied>ειτος\u003C/w>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Cw n=\"10\">ἔζησεν\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cw n=\"15\">ἔτη\u003C/w> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\" n=\"20\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"60\">\u003Cw n=\"25\">ξ\u003C/w>\u003C/num> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\" n=\"30\">·\u003C/g>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"simple-lemmatized\" resp=\"#VF #RC\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"5\" lemma=\"Ἐπαφρόδειτος\">Ἐπαφρόδειτος\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"10\" lemma=\"ζάω\">ἔζησεν\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"15\" lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"25\" lemma=\"ξ\">ξ\u003C/w>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text based on photograph\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"line 2\">\n                        \u003Cnote>lapis: Ἐπαφροειτος\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#martaf #AA\">\n                \u003Cp>Epaphrodeitos lived for 60 years.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                \u003Cp>Epaphrodeitos visse 60 anni.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Korhonen considers the inscription not urban because of the structure of the epitaph and the palaeography. Moreover, the name of the deceased, \u003Cforeign xml:lang=\"grc\">Ἐπαφρόδιτος\u003C/foreign>, is highly attested in Sicily (see LGPN 3A: 145) and in another inscription from Catania (Libertini 1937: 78).\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>2004.0646\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>54.0901\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Korhonen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2004\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>80\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
